Package: conferencestats
Title: General Conference Talk Corpus ('Parquet') and 'tidytext' Pipelines
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Adriel",
    "Casellas",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    email = "adrielcasellas@users.noreply.github.com"
  )
Description: Primary workflow: build or download a versioned General
    Conference talk corpus as compressed Apache 'Parquet', then analyse with
    'tidytext' (tokens, sparse document term matrices, TF-IDF). Builds the
    corpus via the third-party 'generalconference' package when present, or
    download a pre-built 'Parquet' from a URL you configure. Can still ingest
    ad-hoc JSON / CSV exports with 'read_gc_talks()'.
